message.content:
We start by extracting the key data from the provided statements (all numbers refer to the end amounts):

1. Current Assets and Current Liabilities  
 • Total Current Assets = 10,261,562.67  
 • Total Current Liabilities = 1,548,001.20  
 • Current Ratio = Total Current Assets / Total Current Liabilities  
  = 10,261,562.67 / 1,548,001.20  
  ≈ 6.63

2. Gross Profit Margin  
 • Gross Profit = 2,620,023.09  
 • Total Revenue = 5,760,023.09  
 • Gross Profit Margin = (Gross Profit / Total Revenue) × 100  
  = (2,620,023.09 / 5,760,023.09) × 100  
  ≈ 45.42%

3. Debt to Asset Ratio  
 • From the balance sheet, Total Assets = 15,653,266.97 and Total Owner’s Equity = 14,105,265.77.  
 • Total Liabilities = Total Assets − Total Owner’s Equity  
  = 15,653,266.97 − 14,105,265.77  
  = 1,548,001.20  
 • Debt to Asset Ratio = Total Liabilities / Total Assets  
  = 1,548,001.20 / 15,653,266.97  
  ≈ 0.10

4. Net Profit Margin  
 • Net Profit = 1,105,265.77  
 • Net Profit Margin = (Net Profit / Total Revenue) × 100  
  = (1,105,265.77 / 5,760,023.09) × 100  
  ≈ 19.19%

5. Cash to Current Debt Ratio  
 • Cash and Cash Equivalents are given by:
  Cash on Hand = 4,863,237.11  
  Bank Deposits = 3,502,535.57  
  Total Cash = 4,863,237.11 + 3,502,535.57 = 8,365,772.68  
 • Cash to Current Debt Ratio = Total Cash / Total Current Liabilities  
  = 8,365,772.68 / 1,548,001.20  
  ≈ 5.40

6. Free Cash Flow (FCF)  
 • Net Cash Flow from Operating Activities = 803,237.11  
 • Capital Expenditures (here, Purchase of Fixed Assets) = 437,464.43  
 • FCF = Operating Cash Flow − Capital Expenditures  
  = 803,237.11 − 437,464.43  
  = 365,772.68

7. Return on Assets (ROA)  
 • ROA = (Net Profit / Total Assets) × 100  
  = (1,105,265.77 / 15,653,266.97) × 100  
  ≈ 7.06%

Thus, the final solution in the required JSON format is:

{
  "solution": {
    "Current Ratio": "6.63",
    "Gross Profit Margin": "45.42%",
    "Debt to Asset Ratio": "0.10",
    "Net Profit Margin": "19.19%",
    "Cash to Current Debt Ratio": "5.40",
    "Free Cash Flow (FCF)": "365772.68",
    "Return on Assets (ROA)": "7.06%"
  }
}
